#: ../../home/kovid/work/calibre/manual/faq.rst:348
msgid ""
"You will see a list of books in Safari, tap on any book and you will be "
"given the option to either download it, or read it in the browser itself. If"
" you choose to download it, Safari will ask you if you want to open it with "
"iBooks."
msgstr "Verá una lista de libros en Safari, pulse sobre cualquier libro y se mostrarán opciones para descargarlo o leerlo en el navegador. Si elige descargarlo, Safari le preguntará si quiere abrirlo con iBooks."

#: ../../home/kovid/work/calibre/manual/faq.rst:353
msgid "How do I use calibre with my Android phone/tablet or Kindle Fire HD?"
msgstr "¿Cómo utilizo calibre con mi teléfono o tableta Android o mi Kindle Fire HD?"

#: ../../home/kovid/work/calibre/manual/faq.rst:355
msgid ""
"There are two ways that you can connect your Android device to calibre. "
