#: ../../home/kovid/work/calibre/manual/faq.rst:600
msgid ""
"After you have changed all the authors, press the `Recalculate all author "
"sort values` button."
msgstr "Después de haber cambiado todos los autores, pulse el botón :guilabel:`Recalcular todos los valores de orden de autor`."

#: ../../home/kovid/work/calibre/manual/faq.rst:601
#: ../../home/kovid/work/calibre/manual/faq.rst:610
msgid ""
"Press OK, at which point calibre will change the authors in all your books. "
