#: ../../home/kovid/work/calibre/manual/faq.rst:938
msgid ""
"Downloading from the Internet can sometimes result in a corrupted download. "
"If the calibre installer you downloaded is not opening, try downloading it "
"again. If re-downloading it does not work, download it from `an alternate "
"location <https://github.com/kovidgoyal/calibre/releases/latest>`_. If the "
"installer still doesn't work, then something on your computer is preventing "
"it from running."
msgstr "Las descargas de Internet pueden resultar corruptas en ocasiones. Si el instalador de calibre que ha descargado no se abre, pruebe a descargarlo de nuevo. Si esto no funciona, descárguelo de una `ubicación alternativa <https://github.com/kovidgoyal/calibre/releases/latest>`_. Si aún no funciona, algo en el equipo está evitando que se ejecute."

#: ../../home/kovid/work/calibre/manual/faq.rst:940
msgid ""
"Try temporarily disabling your antivirus program (Microsoft Security "
"Essentials, or Kaspersky or Norton or McAfee or whatever). This is most "
"likely the culprit if the upgrade process is hanging in the middle."
msgstr "Pruebe deshabilitar temporalmente el programa antivirus (Microsoft Security Essentials, Kaspersky, Norton, McAfee o el que sea). Éste es probablemente el culpable de que el proceso de actualización se cuelgue a la mitad."

#: ../../home/kovid/work/calibre/manual/faq.rst:941
msgid ""
"Try rebooting your computer and running a registry cleaner like `Wise "
"registry cleaner <http://www.wisecleaner.com>`_."
msgstr "Intente reiniciar el equipo y ejecutar un limpiador del registro como `Wise registry cleaner <http://www.wisecleaner.com>`_."

#: ../../home/kovid/work/calibre/manual/faq.rst:942
msgid ""
"Try a clean install. That is, uninstall calibre, delete :file:`C:\\\\Program"
" Files\\\\Calibre2` (or wherever you previously chose to install calibre). "
"Then re-install calibre. Note that uninstalling does not touch your books or"
" settings."
msgstr "Pruebe una instalación limpia. Esto es, desinstale calibre, elimine :file:`C:\\\\Program Files\\\\Calibre2` (o donde previamente haya decidido instalar calibre). Después reinstale calibre. Tenga en cuenta que la desinstalación no afecta a sus libros o configuraciones."

#: ../../home/kovid/work/calibre/manual/faq.rst:943
msgid ""
"Try downloading the installer with an alternate browser. For example if you "
"are using Internet Explorer, try using Firefox or Chrome instead."
msgstr "Pruebe a descargar el instalador desde otro navegador. Por ejemplo, si está usando Internet Explorer, pruebe con Firefox o Chrome en su lugar."

#: ../../home/kovid/work/calibre/manual/faq.rst:944
msgid ""
"If you get an error about a missing DLL on Windows, then most likely, the "
"permissions on your temporary folder are incorrect. Go to the folder "
